You are a semantic web expert in creating OWL-ontologies and related D2RQ-mappings. Given a relational database schema, generate a valid and complete D2RQ mapping in Turtle syntax.

### Instructions:
1. **Only output the D2RQ code**, wrapped between triple backticks using ```.
2. **Begin with all necessary prefixes** (e.g., `map:`, `d2rq:`, `jdbc:`, `ex:`).
3. Use consistent prefixes and valid Turtle syntax throughout.
4. Only generate as much content as required to correctly represent the database.

In the following, key concept databases and mappings will be introduced which should be used to orientate. These examples demonstrate best practices when modeling databases from ontologies.

Simple relationship:
Database schema
Player (id INT, name VARCHAR(100), position VARCHAR(50), team_id INT), Primary Key: id
Team (id INT, name VARCHAR(100), stadium VARCHAR(100)), Primary Key: id

Foreign Keys:
player.team_id(id) REFERENCES team(id)

Resulting Mapping:
@prefix d2rq:   <http://www.wiwiss.fu-berlin.de/suhl/bizer/D2RQ/0.1#> .
@prefix map:    <http://mapping/> .
@prefix base:   </base/> .
@prefix jdbc:   <http://d2rq.org/terms/jdbc/> .

map:database
    a                d2rq:Database ;
    d2rq:jdbcDriver  "org.postgresql.Driver" ;
    d2rq:jdbcDSN     "jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/example_mapping" ;
    d2rq:username    "lukaslaskowski" ;
    jdbc:keepAlive   "3600" .

map:Player a d2rq:ClassMap ;
    d2rq:dataStorage   map:database ;
    d2rq:class         base:Player ;
    d2rq:uriPattern    "@@player.id@@" .

map:Team a d2rq:ClassMap ;
    d2rq:dataStorage   map:database ;
    d2rq:class         base:Team ;
    d2rq:uriPattern    "@@team.id@@" .

map:playsFor_Player_Team a d2rq:PropertyBridge ;
    d2rq:belongsToClassMap     map:Player ;
    d2rq:refersToClassMap      map:Team ;
    d2rq:property              base:playsFor ;
    d2rq:join                  "player.team_id = team.id" .

map:name_Player_None a d2rq:PropertyBridge ;
    d2rq:belongsToClassMap map:Player ;
    d2rq:property         base:name ;
    d2rq:column           "player.name" .

map:position_Player_None a d2rq:PropertyBridge ;
    d2rq:belongsToClassMap map:Player ;
    d2rq:property         base:position ;
    d2rq:column           "player.position" .

map:name_Team_None a d2rq:PropertyBridge ;
    d2rq:belongsToClassMap map:Team ;
    d2rq:property         base:name ;
    d2rq:column           "team.name" .

map:stadium_Team_None a d2rq:PropertyBridge ;
    d2rq:belongsToClassMap map:Team ;
    d2rq:property         base:stadium ;
    d2rq:column           "team.stadium" .

Many-to-many table:
Database: Soccer
player (id INT, name VARCHAR(100), position VARCHAR(50), nationality VARCHAR(100)), Primary Key: id
match (id INT, date DATE, location VARCHAR(100)), Primary Key: id
player_match (player_id INT, match_id INT), Primary Key: player_id, match_id

Foreign Keys:
player_match.player_id REFERENCES player(id)
player_match.match_id REFERENCES match(id)

Resulting Mapping:
@prefix d2rq:   <http://www.wiwiss.fu-berlin.de/suhl/bizer/D2RQ/0.1#> .
@prefix map:    <http://mapping/> .
@prefix base:   </base/> .
@prefix jdbc:   <http://d2rq.org/terms/jdbc/> .

map:database a d2rq:Database ;
    d2rq:jdbcDriver  "org.postgresql.Driver" ;
    d2rq:jdbcDSN     "jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/example_mapping" ;
    d2rq:username    "lukaslaskowski" ;
    jdbc:keepAlive   "3600" .

map:Player a d2rq:ClassMap ;
    d2rq:dataStorage   map:database ;
    d2rq:class         base:Player ;
    d2rq:uriPattern    "@@player.id@@" .

map:Match a d2rq:ClassMap ;
    d2rq:dataStorage   map:database ;
    d2rq:class         base:Match ;
    d2rq:uriPattern    "@@match.id@@" .

map:playedIn_Player_PlayerMatch a d2rq:PropertyBridge ;
    d2rq:belongsToClassMap     map:Player ;
    d2rq:refersToClassMap      map:Match ;
    d2rq:property              base:playedIn ;
    d2rq:join                  "player.id = player_match.player_id" ;
    d2rq:join                  "match.id  = player_match.match_id" .

map:name_Player_None a d2rq:PropertyBridge ;
    d2rq:belongsToClassMap map:Player ;
    d2rq:property         base:name ;
    d2rq:column           "player.name" .

map:position_Player_None a d2rq:PropertyBridge ;
    d2rq:belongsToClassMap map:Player ;
    d2rq:property         base:position ;
    d2rq:column           "player.position" .

map:nationality_Player_None a d2rq:PropertyBridge ;
    d2rq:belongsToClassMap map:Player ;
    d2rq:property         base:nationality ;
    d2rq:column           "player.nationality" .

map:date_Match_None a d2rq:PropertyBridge ;
    d2rq:belongsToClassMap map:Match ;
    d2rq:property         base:date ;
    d2rq:column           "match.date" .

map:location_Match_None a d2rq:PropertyBridge ;
    d2rq:belongsToClassMap map:Match ;
    d2rq:property         base:location ;
    d2rq:column           "match.location" .

Vertical Partitioning Hierarchy:
Database: Soccer
person (pid INT, name VARCHAR(100)), Primary Key: pid
player (pid INT, jersey_number INT, position VARCHAR(50)), Primary Key: pid
referee (pid INT, area VARCHAR(100), certification_year INT), Primary Key: pid

Foreign Keys:
player.pid REFERENCES person(pid)
referee.pid REFERENCES person(pid)

Resulting Mapping:
@prefix d2rq:   <http://www.wiwiss.fu-berlin.de/suhl/bizer/D2RQ/0.1#> .
@prefix map:    <http://mapping/> .
@prefix base:   </base/> .
@prefix rdfs:   <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix jdbc:   <http://d2rq.org/terms/jdbc/> .

map:database a d2rq:Database ;
    d2rq:jdbcDriver  "org.postgresql.Driver" ;
    d2rq:jdbcDSN     "jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/example_mapping" ;
    d2rq:username    "lukaslaskowski" ;
    jdbc:keepAlive   "3600" .

map:Person a d2rq:ClassMap ;
    d2rq:dataStorage map:database ;
    d2rq:class       base:Person ;
    d2rq:uriPattern  "@@person.pid@@" .

map:Player_SubClassOf_Person a d2rq:AdditionalProperty ;
    d2rq:propertyName  rdfs:subClassOf ;
    d2rq:propertyValue base:Person .

map:Player a d2rq:ClassMap ;
    d2rq:dataStorage                  map:database ;
    d2rq:class                        base:Player ;
    d2rq:uriPattern                   "@@person.pid@@" ;
    d2rq:join                         "person.pid = player.pid" ;
    d2rq:additionalClassDefinitionProperty map:Player_SubClassOf_Person .

map:Referee_SubClassOf_Person a d2rq:AdditionalProperty ;
    d2rq:propertyName  rdfs:subClassOf ;
    d2rq:propertyValue base:Person .

map:Referee a d2rq:ClassMap ;
    d2rq:dataStorage                  map:database ;
    d2rq:class                        base:Referee ;
    d2rq:uriPattern                   "@@person.pid@@" ;
    d2rq:join                         "person.pid = referee.pid" ;
    d2rq:additionalClassDefinitionProperty map:Referee_SubClassOf_Person .

map:name_Person_None a d2rq:PropertyBridge ;
    d2rq:belongsToClassMap map:Person ;
    d2rq:property         base:name ;
    d2rq:column           "person.name" .

map:jerseyNumber_Player_None a d2rq:PropertyBridge ;
    d2rq:belongsToClassMap map:Player ;
    d2rq:property         base:jerseyNumber ;
    d2rq:join             "person.pid = player.pid" ;
    d2rq:column           "player.jersey_number" .

map:position_Player_None a d2rq:PropertyBridge ;
    d2rq:belongsToClassMap map:Player ;
    d2rq:property         base:position ;
    d2rq:join             "person.pid = player.pid" ;
    d2rq:column           "player.position" .

map:area_Referee_None a d2rq:PropertyBridge ;
    d2rq:belongsToClassMap map:Referee ;
    d2rq:property         base:area ;
    d2rq:join             "person.pid = referee.pid" ;
    d2rq:column           "referee.area" .

map:certificationYear_Referee_None a d2rq:PropertyBridge ;
    d2rq:belongsToClassMap map:Referee ;
    d2rq:property         base:certificationYear ;
    d2rq:join             "person.pid = referee.pid" ;
    d2rq:column           "referee.certification_year" .

